      "description": "<p>You have an <strong>Ultima Power</strong> you can perform by filling up its clock, with the following triggers:</p><ul><li><p>Fill 1 section each time you lose Hit Points in a round, unless that loss was self-inflicted.</p></li><li><p>Fill 1 section when you enter Crisis for the first time in a conflict.</p></li><li><p>Fill 1 section when you hit with an attack or spell and the <strong>result of the accuracy check was an odd number</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Unleashing the zero effect erases all sections of the Zero Clock.</p></li></ul>",
